ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of LISE des GRENIERS of Granby, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective February 1, 2008, in the place of Johanne Bouchard.
